      "doc": "<p>Stores a response field value under a symbolic name.</p>\n<p>The value can be used later via <code>$MEM{name}</code> expansion.</p>\n<p>Examples:</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tr>\n<td>RESTMemorizeValue</td>\n<td>data.token</td>\n<td>TOKEN</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>RESTMemorizeValue</td>\n<td>data.id</td>\n<td>USER_ID</td>\n</tr>\n</table>",
