      "doc": "<p>Sets the context path for subsequent SetValue/VerifyValue calls.</p>\n<p>Fields are resolved relative to the context path. Each call replaces the previous context (flat, no stack).</p>\n<p>Examples:</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tr>\n<td>RESTSetContext</td>\n<td>customer</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>RESTSetContext</td>\n<td>customer.address</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>RESTSetContext</td>\n<td>items[0]</td>\n</tr>\n</table>",
