      "doc": "<p>Starts a REST service session.</p>\n<p>Loads the YAML configuration for the given service name and initialises the REST context with base URL, content type, authentication, and SSL settings.</p>\n<p>The optional <code>env</code> parameter specifies an environment file (YAML) whose values replace <code>${VAR}</code> placeholders in the service YAML. If omitted, placeholders are resolved from OS environment variables.</p>\n<p>Examples:</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tr>\n<td>RESTStart</td>\n<td>NotesAPI</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>RESTStart</td>\n<td>NotesAPI</td>\n<td>env-test</td>\n</tr>\n</table>",
